OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fspells of sunshine around this
OL,7,Fevening, before a band of cloud and
OL,8,Frain accompanied by blustery winds
OL,9,Fspreads eastward overnight. A milder
OL,10,Fnight than of late.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FOvernight rain clearing to
OL,13,Fthe northeast, leaving a mix of sunny
OL,14,Fspells and blustery showers on
OL,15,FTuesday. Some of the showers
OL,16,Fpotentially heavy with a risk of
OL,17,Fthunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
