OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FLighter winds on Wednesday but still
OL,7,Fwith plenty of showers. Turning drier
OL,8,Fand brighter from Thursday, with sunny
OL,9,Fspells for many. Feeling much warmer
OL,10,Fby Friday with temperatures above
OL,11,Faverage.
